data.description: Welcome Home! Completely remodeled 2 story, in an adorable Watertown Neighborhood, Close to Fort Drum, and all the towns' amenities. Everything is brand new. walk into a big spacious living room, perfect for entertaining. Large kitchen, with all new appliances, with two bedrooms downstairs, one having an attached full bath, and a full laundry room. Upstairs you will find 3 additional bedrooms, another living room and a bonus room or possible 6th  bedroom. Pack your bags! this home is waiting for a family to make it their own, and to make memories in for years to come.
